# No Co-authored-by trailer

Never add this line anywhere in this repository:

```
Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>
```

This applies to:

- Git commit messages and commit bodies
- Pull request descriptions
- Source files, comments, docs, and changelogs

Write commit messages with only the human-authored content. Do not append co-author trailers for Cursor or any agent.
